'''鲁希恩·麦克唐纳'''（{{lang-en|Rusheen McDonald}}，{{bd|1992年|8月17日||}}）是一名牙买加男子短跑运动员。

麦克唐纳在牙买加奥运会选拔赛400米项目以45.1秒排名第二，获得[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]资格。<ref>{{cite web|last=O'Neal|first=Reid|title=Dane Hyatt had more left in the tank – coach George Williams|url=http://trackledger.com/2012/07/10/dane-hyatt-had-more-left-in-the-tank-coach-george-williams/|work=trackledger.com|accessdate=2012-08-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222001526/http://trackledger.com/2012/07/10/dane-hyatt-had-more-left-in-the-tank-coach-george-williams/|archivedate=2014-02-22}}</ref>他在该届奥运参加400米赛跑和4×400米接力两个小项。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rusheen McDonald – Athletics – Olympic Athlete|url=http://www.london2012.com/athlete/mcdonald-rusheen-1297691/|work=London 2012|accessdate=2012-08-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822081553/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/mcdonald-rusheen-1297691/|archivedate=2012-08-22}}</ref>其中在400米预赛中，他以46.67秒在他所在小组中排名第四，未能晋级半决赛。<ref>{{cite web|title=Hyatt qualifies for 400 semis, Gonzalez, McDonald out of luck|url=http://go-jamaica.com/news/read_article.php?id=39032|work=go-jamaica.com|accessdate=2012-08-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222210919/http://go-jamaica.com/news/read_article.php?id=39032|archivedate=2014-02-22}}</ref>

